      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"ghost items\" idea is interesting. I'll have the IT team look into the transaction logs and the UoM settings to see if there are any synchronization errors or unposted picks. \n\nOne thing though, even when we check the logs, it's hard to pin down exactly when or where a single unit goes missing. It's just these tiny, unexplained gaps that appear out of nowhere. Is there anything else—maybe something more subtle in the logistics flow or the way the bins are organized—that could cause these little bits of inventory to just seem like they've vanished?",
